text: Adhi'adeye or Ade Adeye (Somali: Adhi Cadeeye) is a town in the Sool region of Somaliland.http://www.geographic.org/geographic_names/name.php?uni=-4554026&fid;=5791&c;=somalia It is 30 miles northwest of Las Anod, the regional capital of Sool.https://www.unicef.org/somalia/UNICEFSomRvwJan04fnl.PDFhttp://www.geographic.org/geographic_names/name.php?uni=-4554026&fid;=5791&c;=somalia ==References== Category:Populated places in Somalia
title: Adhi'adeye
